        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, so as I have done, and have now said. As I have begun, I will go on: the present devout affections shall not pass away like the morning cloud, but shine more and more like the morning sun. Or, ",
        "children": []
